body: Thanks @tobegit3hub . In the original issue, I did not realize you were referring to the contrib.learn utility. As that code is deprecated, we do not make ongoing changes. Have you tried with `tf.estimator.export.build_parsing_serving_input_receiver_fn`? Does that util have the same problem?
